Distribution. This tropical inshore species is known from southern Indonesian waters, the Sulu Sea, (
Hansen 1910
), the northern and southern Philippines (
W.M. Tattersall 1951
) and the Ryukyu Islands between Japan and Taiwan (
Fukuoka & Murano 1997
). It may also occur in the Singapore Strait (
O .S. Tattersall 1960
). In Australia it has been found in northern Queensland, in Princess Charlotte Bay (
W.M. Tattersall 1928
) and the Great Barrier Reef at Low Isles (
W.M. Tattersall 1936 a
), Heron Island (Fenton 1982 ) and Davies Reef (
Carleton & Hamner 1989
).
